<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870119-0031 </DOCNO><HL> Business Brief:Bonanza Resources Ltd.</HL><DD> 01/19/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> T.BNZ T.POCTENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM) </IN><TEXT>   BONANZA RESOURCES LTD., a Calgary, Alberta-based oil and gas company, said its shareholders at a special meeting approved a previously reported proposal to sell all the company's Canadian oil and gas assets to Poco Petroleums Ltd. of Calgary. Bonanza said its holders also approved a name change to CanCapital Corp. and a consolidation of common shares on a 1-for-2 basis, as well as other changes to the company's capitalization. </TEXT></DOC>